===Etymology===
After the genus ''[[Fuchsia]]'', itself named after [[w:Leonhart Fuchs|Leonhart Fuchs]], German botanist.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ˈfjuːʃə/|lang=en}} 
* {{rhymes|uːʃə|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A popular garden plant, of the [[genus]] ''[[Fuchsia]]'', of the ''Onagraceae'' [[family]], [[shrub]]s with red, pink or purple [[flower]]s.
# A purplish-red [[color|colour]], the color of [[fuchsin]], an aniline [[dye]].
#: {{color panel|web fuchsia ([[magenta]])|FF00FF}}
#: {{color panel|fashion magenta (Hollywood cerise)|F400A1}}

